posting_body: ['We are currently offering virtual tours.', 'Please use the link in this ad to visit our website and set up a tour today or give us a call!', 'The Commons at Windsor Gardens', '624 Walpole St., Norwood, MA, 02062', 'Call Now - (781) 819-5321 x 8', 'Interested in more information?', 'See link below:', '<URL>', 'Inspired Features and Superb Amenities', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 730 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'The Commons at Windsor Gardens features outstanding amenities and stylish apartments in Norwood, MA.', 'Select apartments include hardwood flooring, stainless steel appliances, and an in-home washer and dryer.', 'Enjoy access to on-site amenities like tennis courts, volleyball courts, swimming pools, and a fitness facility.', 'With easy access to I-95, Route 128 and a Commuter Rail stop right on the premises, Boston commuters can walk out their front door and be whisked into South Station in just 25 minutes.', 'Located on Walpole Street / Route 1A in historic Norwood, The Commons at Windsor Gardens is just a short distance from many dining, nightlife, shopping, and recreational destinations.', 'Schedule a tour today and experience stylish apartment living in Norwood.', 'We are currently offering self-guided tours.', 'Pet Policy', 'Dogs Allowed Breed restrictions', '$75 Monthly Pet Rent', '2 Pet Limit', 'Cats Allowed', '$50 Monthly Pet Rent', '2 Pet Limit', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday: 10:00AM-5:30PM', 'Saturday: 10:30AM-4:30PM', 'qPsTKTdN1FMh']
